subject: Horse Racing
Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Awards, Decorations and Honors
Horses
Triple Crown (Horse Racing)
lead_paragraph: The filly Rachel Alexandra took home horse racing’s top prize, the Eclipse Award for Horse of the Year, receiving 130 votes to 99 for Zenyatta.
